      "title": "Urea under Indian credit line arrives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Forty-six thousand metric tons of urea fertilizer\u00a0 under the Indian credit line reached Sri Lanka recently. The consignment was taken to government warehouses in Colombo yesterday. This was the first time a consignment of fertilizer came to Sri Lanka since the ban imposed by President Gotabaya Rajapaksa\u2019s administration. Pix by Pradeep Pathirana"
